    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/0f1987ba7349c7fe6ac5bed2ce698609_7007058917544811085.png",
                "id": "talent28173",
                "key": "喧嘩屋傳說",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "喧嘩屋傳說"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">阿丑</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂神之怪力</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂神之怪力</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>造成的傷害+1。如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>至少為2，則少花費1個<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">無色元素</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/04fdb866d761fb643bfdb71186ba8280_7854162977866508977.png",
                "id": "talent19182",
                "key": "魔殺絕技·赤牛發破！",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔殺絕技·赤牛發破！"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">怒目鬼王</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">怒目鬼王</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻擊</span>造成的傷害+1，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色普通攻擊後：</span>為其附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂神之怪力</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">亂神之怪力</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>造成的傷害+1。如果<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>至少為2，則少花費1個<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">無色元素</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/1211407f3b204194af8f313d11df19bf_4043992153957952208.png",
                "id": "talent69652",
                "key": "最惡鬼王·一斗轟臨！！",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "最惡鬼王·一斗轟臨！！"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1，耗盡時不棄置此牌。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召喚物在場期間可觸發1次：</span>我方出戰角色受到傷害後，為荒瀧一斗附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">亂神之怪力</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>棄置此牌，造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素傷害</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">亂神之怪力</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色進行重擊時：</span>造成的傷害+1。如果<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>至少為2，則少花費1個<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">無色元素</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：1（可疊加，最多疊加到3次）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6019840579019480206.png",
                "id": "talent93097",
                "key": "阿丑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/17/125391187/ea059a3f7bee2dea6bcee851752339c3_1824657042999919197.png",
                "title": "阿丑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（冰）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（水）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（火）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結晶（雷）</span>：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8042833823530259560.png",
                "id": "talent84764",
                "key": "岩元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">重擊</span></strong></p><p>我方元素骰總數為偶數時進行的「普通攻擊」，視為「重擊」。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8828968985310573894.png",
